title: A1347 No power on.
message: Hello i have this Mac mini no power on, what can i do?

title: A1347 No power on.
message:
Start posting some usefull information.
Not easy to work on Mini without schematic/boardview.
But you should be able to find the main power rail and at least 3V3_S5 coil.

Check diode mode on main power rail.
If short/low, then compare with all big coils.
